fcardsaver (1.2.5) precise; urgency=low

  * Win32 build documentation corrections, removed trailing spaces from several files.
  * New control for 'data-root' configuration parameter; fixes #3.
  * Updated Hanazono font URL for Win32 build to version 2013-02-22.
  * Fixes and additions in BUILD.win32 file.
  * Ignore QtCreator-created configuration and extra Win32 build scripts.
  * Win32 example build script now accepts additional make parameters.
  * Ignore subdirectory web/ (used for gh-pages).
  * Fix Win32 headers for SHGetFolderPath() (MinGW 4.7 removed it from <shlwapi.h>).
  * Removed deprecated qVariantValue() and qVariantCanConvert() calls.
  * Change NSIS script to use "libraries.list" for list of files to install/delete (closes issue #6).
  * Implemented new flashcard file instruction "protect" (closes issue #4).
  * Documentation on configuration parameters is split into a separate manpage.
  * Initial set of changes in preparation to Qt5.

 -- Alec Kojaev <alec@kojaev.name>  Sun, 14 Jul 2013 21:18:57 +0400

